<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     KAST
════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="section section-alt" id="kast">
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-k">Platform 01</div>
  <h2 class="sh">KAST Affiliate Program</h2>
  <p class="ss">Performance-based, 4-level multi-tier program. Affiliates earn instant USDC commissions on card activations, physical card purchases, and recurring lifetime transaction volume — plus KAST Points convertible at the Q2 2026 TGE.</p>

  <div class="platform-header ph-k">
    <div class="ph-badge ph-badge-k">K</div>
    <div class="ph-right">
      <div class="ph-name">KAST</div>
      <div class="ph-tag">kast.xyz/affiliate — Open registration · Real-time dashboard · Instant USDC</div>
      <div class="ph-body">Breadth of card tiers (Standard → Luxe) creates flexible commission surfaces at every level. Lifetime recurring transaction commissions reward long-term loyalty over single activations. Dual-stack incentive (cash now + token upside) is the primary differentiator for KOL recruitment. A live competitive leaderboard adds daily USDC prize pools on top of the base commission structure.</div>
      <div class="ph-chips">
        <span class="ph-chip chip-k">Open Registration</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-k">Instant USDC</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-k">Lifetime Transaction Commissions</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-k">KAST Points → TGE Q2 2026</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-k">Real-Time Dashboard</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-orange">2× Commission Promo Active</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tier Table -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-k" style="margin-bottom:12px">Commission Tier Structure</div>
  <div class="tier-wrap">
    <table class="tier-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th>Threshold</th>
          <th>Spend Bonus (Standard)</th>
          <th>Physical Card — Standard</th>
          <th>Physical Card — Premium / Luxe</th>
          <th>Transaction Commission</th>
          <th>KAST Points Bonus</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-k">Level 1</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-k">5 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">$8</span><span class="tier-sub">per active user</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">20%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">5%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of spend volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">5,000</span><span class="tier-sub">KAST points</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-k">Level 2</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-k">50 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">$10</span><span class="tier-sub">per active user</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">50%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.20%</span><span class="tier-sub">of spend volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">5,000</span><span class="tier-sub">KAST points</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-k">Level 3</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-k">100 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">$10</span><span class="tier-sub">per active user</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">60%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.25%</span><span class="tier-sub">of spend volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">5,000</span><span class="tier-sub">KAST points</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-k">Level 4</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-k">500 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">$10</span><span class="tier-sub">per active user</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">80%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">15%</span><span class="tier-sub">of card fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.35%</span><span class="tier-sub">of spend volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">5,000</span><span class="tier-sub">KAST points</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-k">VIP <span class="invite-tag">Invite Only</span></span></td>
          <td>Not disclosed</td>
          <td colspan="5" style="color:var(--t4);font-style:italic">Terms not publicly available — negotiated individually</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--t4);margin-bottom:32px">* <strong>Active user definition:</strong> a referred user who completes ≥$100 in total KAST card spending (single or cumulative transactions). Both the spend bonus and doubled 2× promo commission trigger at this milestone.</p>

  <!-- Commission Streams -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-k" style="margin-bottom:12px">Commission Streams</div>
  <div class="stream-grid">
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-k">💳</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-k">Spend Bonus</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">$8–10</div>
      <div class="stream-title">Per active user (≥$100 card spend)</div>
      <div class="stream-body">Flat cash bonus paid when a referred user hits the $100 spend threshold for the first time. Amount scales from $8 at Level 1 to $10 at Levels 2–4.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-instant">⚡ Instant USDC</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-k">🪙</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-k">Physical Card Commission</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">20–80%</div>
      <div class="stream-title">% of card issuance fee (Standard tier)</div>
      <div class="stream-body">Paid on physical card purchases. Standard cards: 20% at L1 scaling to 80% at L4. Premium/Luxe cards: 5–15%. Higher percentages reward volume referrers significantly.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-instant">⚡ Instant USDC</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-k">🔁</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-k">Transaction Commission</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">0.10–0.35%</div>
      <div class="stream-title">% of referred users' card spend — recurring, lifetime</div>
      <div class="stream-body">Earned on every transaction made by referred users forever. No expiry. The most valuable stream for affiliates with large, active referral bases over the long term.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-instant">⚡ Instant USDC</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-k">👥</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-k">Tier 2 — Multi-Level</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">+10%</div>
      <div class="stream-title">Of earnings generated by your referrals' own referrals</div>
      <div class="stream-body">Compounding incentive for affiliates who recruit other active affiliates. Earns 10% on top of whatever a direct referral earns from their own sub-network.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-instant">⚡ Instant USDC</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-k">🏆</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-k">KAST Points Stack</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">5,000+</div>
      <div class="stream-title">Points per tier unlock + % of referral points</div>
      <div class="stream-body">5,000 KAST Points per tier. Plus 30% of L1 referrals' points and 6% of L2 referrals' points. Points convert to KAST token at the Q2 2026 TGE (notional value rose $0.03 → $0.10 across seasons).</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-tge">🔮 Q2 2026 TGE</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-o">🎯</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-o">Active Promo — 2× Commission</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">2×</div>
      <div class="stream-title">Doubled commission on first $100 spend — indefinite</div>
      <div class="stream-body">When a referred user hits the $100 spend milestone for the first time, the affiliate earns 2× their standard tier commission. No cap. No end date. Applies at every tier automatically.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-weekly">🔥 No expiry · No cap</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Leaderboard -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-k" style="margin-bottom:12px">Referral Leaderboard</div>
  <div class="promo-grid">
    <div class="promo-card promo-2x">
      <div class="promo-label pl-white">Live Leaderboard</div>
      <div class="promo-title pt-white">Daily · Weekly · Monthly · All-Time rankings</div>
      <div class="promo-body pb-white">A competitive leaderboard launched alongside the referral program upgrade. Tracks affiliate rankings across four timeframes. Prizes paid daily in USDC — snapshots lock at midnight UTC, prizes credited the next day.</div>
      <div class="promo-body pb-white" style="margin-top:10px">Minimum <span class="promo-highlight">500 referral points</span> required to appear. Ties resolved by total KAST Points across all categories.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="promo-card promo-lb">
      <div class="promo-label pl-k">Daily Prizes</div>
      <div class="promo-title pt-navy">Top 3 daily prize payouts — USDC</div>
      <div class="lb-prizes">
        <div class="lb-prize lb-1st">
          <div class="lb-rank">1st Place</div>
          <div class="lb-amount">$1,000</div>
          <div class="lb-cur">USDC / day</div>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-prize">
          <div class="lb-rank">2nd Place</div>
          <div class="lb-amount">$200</div>
          <div class="lb-cur">USDC / day</div>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-prize">
          <div class="lb-rank">3rd Place</div>
          <div class="lb-amount">$100</div>
          <div class="lb-cur">USDC / day</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="promo-body pb-dark" style="margin-top:14px;font-size:11px">Max total exclusive bonus potential across all mechanics: <strong>up to $5,000 USDC</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Meta -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-k" style="margin-bottom:12px">Payout & Access Details</div>
  <div class="meta-grid">
    <div class="meta-card">
      <div class="meta-label">Payout</div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Currency</span><span class="meta-val">USDC only</span></div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Speed</span><span class="meta-val">Instant on qualifying event</span></div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Transaction commission timing</span><span class="meta-val">Recurring — no stated settlement lag</span></div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Tracking</span><span class="meta-val">Real-time dashboard</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-card">
      <div class="meta-label">Access</div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Registration</span><span class="meta-val">Open — anyone can join</span></div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">KYC requirement (affiliate)</span><span class="meta-val">Not stated</span></div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">VIP / Elite tier</span><span class="meta-val">Invite-only — criteria not published</span></div>
      <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Primary target</span><span class="meta-val">Creators, community builders, crypto enthusiasts</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="div">

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     REDOTPAY
════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="section" id="redotpay">
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-r">Platform 02</div>
  <h2 class="sh">Redotpay Affiliate Program</h2>
  <p class="ss">Tiered performance program explicitly targeting institutions, B2B partners, KOLs, and professional marketers. Runs four parallel distribution channels simultaneously — generating multiple parallel growth vectors and contributing to 3M+ users added in a single calendar year.</p>

  <div class="platform-header ph-r">
    <div class="ph-badge ph-badge-r">R</div>
    <div class="ph-right">
      <div class="ph-name">Redotpay</div>
      <div class="ph-tag">redotpay.com/affiliates — KYC required · 160+ countries · USDT / BTC / ETH / bank transfer</div>
      <div class="ph-body">Utility-first, institutional scale. The four-program distribution stack (Referral + KOL + Affiliate + Angels) drives parallel acquisition vectors. Three public tiers: LV1 (0–9 referrals), LV2 (10–29), LV3 (30+) — with LV3 top-end rates and Redot Angels terms negotiated. The $100 physical card issuance fee — highest in the category — generates high per-activation payouts but is a documented acquisition suppressor. Transaction commissions settle on a Net-7 basis upon request, with a $100 minimum payout threshold — the 30-day lag cited earlier reflects the default settlement cycle.</div>
      <div class="ph-chips">
        <span class="ph-chip chip-r">KYC Required</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-r">160+ Countries</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-r">Multi-Currency Payouts</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-r">4 Parallel Programs</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-r">Instant Card Activation Payout</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-r">Lifetime Cookie Tracking</span>
        <span class="ph-chip chip-orange">Min Payout $100 · Net-7 ⚠</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tier Table -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-r" style="margin-bottom:12px">Commission Tier Structure</div>
  <div class="tier-wrap">
    <table class="tier-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th>Threshold</th>
          <th>Card Issuance Commission</th>
          <th>Example — Virtual Card ($10)</th>
          <th>Transaction Commission</th>
          <th>Example — Per $1,000 Spend</th>
          <th>Secondary (Tier 2)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-r">LV1</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-r">0–9 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">20%</span><span class="tier-sub">of issuance fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">2 USDT</span><span class="tier-sub">instant on activation</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.05%</span><span class="tier-sub">of spend volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.5 USDT</span><span class="tier-sub">per $1,000 transacted</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of referral's commission</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-r">LV2</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-r">10–29 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">25%</span><span class="tier-sub">of issuance fee</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">2.5 USDT</span><span class="tier-sub">instant on activation</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">0.10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of spend volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">1 USDT</span><span class="tier-sub">per $1,000 transacted</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of referral's commission</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-r">LV3</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-threshold tt-r">≥30 referrals</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">Up to 40%</span><span class="tier-sub">published ceiling</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">Up to 4 USDT</span><span class="tier-sub">exact rate scales with volume</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">Higher</span><span class="tier-sub">exact rate not publicly disclosed</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">Scales up</span><span class="tier-sub">from LV2 baseline</span></td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">10%</span><span class="tier-sub">of referral's commission</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><span class="tier-label tier-label-r">Redot Angels <span class="invite-tag">Invite Only</span></span></td>
          <td>Performance-based invitation</td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">Above ceiling</span><span class="tier-sub">individually negotiated</span></td>
          <td>Negotiated</td>
          <td>Negotiated</td>
          <td>Negotiated</td>
          <td><span class="tier-highlight">10%+</span><span class="tier-sub">negotiated</span></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--t4);margin-bottom:32px">LV1–LV3 tier thresholds and LV1/LV2 commission amounts are publicly confirmed. LV3 top-end rates and Redot Angels terms are not published and are negotiated individually. Physical card payout example at LV1: 20% × $100 = <strong>20 USDT</strong>. At LV2: 25% × $100 = <strong>25 USDT</strong>. Min payout across all tiers: <strong>$100</strong>. Settlement: <strong>Net-7 upon request</strong>.</p>

  <!-- Commission Streams -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-r" style="margin-bottom:12px">Three Commission Streams</div>
  <div class="stream-grid">
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-r">💳</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-r">Card Activation Commission</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">20–40%</div>
      <div class="stream-title">% of card issuance fee — on every card order</div>
      <div class="stream-body">Virtual card: $10 issuance fee. Physical card: $100 — the highest in the category. Commission = tier % × issuance fee. The $100 physical card generates the largest per-activation payout in the competitor set.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-instant">⚡ Instant USDT</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-r">🔁</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-r">Transaction (Payment) Commission</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">0.05–0.10%+</div>
      <div class="stream-title">% of card spend volume — scales by tier</div>
      <div class="stream-body">LV1: 0.05% (0.5 USDT per $1,000 spend). LV2: 0.10% (1 USDT per $1,000 spend). LV3: higher, not publicly disclosed. Net-7 settlement upon request with a $100 minimum payout threshold — default cycle is 30 days if not requested.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-30d">⏱ Net-7 on request · $100 min</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stream-card">
      <div class="stream-icon si-r">👥</div>
      <div class="stream-label sl-r">Secondary (Tier 2) Commission</div>
      <div class="stream-rate">10%</div>
      <div class="stream-title">Of your direct referral's own commission earnings</div>
      <div class="stream-body">When your direct referral recruits their own users, you earn 10% of that referral's commission income. Compounding incentive for affiliates building sub-networks. Matches KAST's Tier 2 rate.</div>
      <span class="stream-timing st-30d">⏱ 30-day settlement</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Four Programs -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-r" style="margin-bottom:12px">Four Parallel Distribution Programs</div>
  <div class="four-grid">
    <div class="four-card">
      <div class="four-num">Program 01</div>
      <div class="four-title">Referral Program</div>
      <div class="four-body">Standard invite link and code, open to all KYC-verified accounts. The widest-reach channel — generates organic word-of-mouth at no incremental cost. $5 sign-up bonus for new users activating via referral code.</div>
      <div class="four-tag">Open to all users</div>
    </div>
    <div class="four-card">
      <div class="four-num">Program 02</div>
      <div class="four-title">KOL Program</div>
      <div class="four-body">Targets creators and influencers with existing crypto-native audiences. Elevated commission rates, negotiated terms, co-marketing support. Primary driver of Redotpay's volume growth — explained as the mechanism behind 3M users in one calendar year.</div>
      <div class="four-tag">Application required</div>
    </div>
    <div class="four-card">
      <div class="four-num">Program 03</div>
      <div class="four-title">Affiliate Program</div>
      <div class="four-body">Performance-based, tiered structure for professional marketers. The formal affiliate track with the published LV1 (0–9) → LV2 (10–29) → LV3 (30+) ladder. Transaction commissions scale from 0.05% at LV1 to 0.10% at LV2. Net-7 settlement upon request; $100 minimum payout threshold.</div>
      <div class="four-tag">Performance-based</div>
    </div>
    <div class="four-card four-invite">
      <div class="four-num">Program 04</div>
      <div class="four-title">Redot Angels</div>
      <div class="four-body">Invite-only tier for the highest-performing affiliates. Above-Exclusive commission rates, exclusive event access, co-branded campaigns. The "Redot Angels" name signals status but appears to deliver limited community infrastructure beyond elevated rates.</div>
      <div class="four-tag">Elite · Event Access</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Meta -->
  <div class="eyebrow eyebrow-r" style="margin-bottom:12px">Payout & Access Details</div>
  <div class="meta-grid">
    <div class="meta-card">
      <div class="meta-label">Payout</div>
